
=Bio=

Grazzini is a journalist and a writer specialized in economics. He writes for Corriere della Sera  and other newspapers. He published The Good of Everyone. The [[Sharing Economy as a Way Out of the Crisis]] (Editori Internazionali Riuniti, 2011), and Knowledge Economy Beyond Capitalism, (Codice Edizioni, 2008).


